title: CoinDesk 20 Performance Update: Uniswap (UNI) Gains 6.2%, Leading Index Higher
author: CoinDesk Indices
summary: NEAR Protocol (NEAR) was also among the top performers, rising 5.7% from Wednesday.
content:
CoinDesk Indices presents its daily market update, highlighting the performance of leaders and laggards in the CoinDesk 20 Index.

The CoinDesk 20 is currently trading at 3264.85, up 2.0% (+63.87) since 4 p.m. ET on Wednesday.

Nineteen of 20 assets are trading higher.

Leaders: UNI (+6.2%) and NEAR (+5.7%).

Laggards: AAVE (+0.0%) and BTC (+1.2%).

The CoinDesk 20 is a broad-based index traded on multiple platforms in several regions globally.

llm_analysis.reasoning: The CoinDesk 20 Index rose 2.0% with 19 of 20 assets trading higher, led by significant gains in UNI (+6.2%) and NEAR (+5.7%).
